CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 1, 1958, pg. A19, reads: "High-Honor Students - These high-honor students were the four commencement speakers who were graduated from Westinghouse High School, Jan. 24. Left to right, they are Fred DeRubertis, Dorothy Adams, Edwin Roberson and James Marino. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Westinghouse High School honor student graduates, left to right: Fred DeRubertis, Dorothy Adams, Edwin Roberson, and James Marino
